--  render uses real Lucide spritesheet rects instead of mismatched
--  Roblox CDN ids. The library is cached under Library._Lucide so
--  consumer scripts can call Library:GetIcon(name) too.
--
--  applyIcon(imgLabel, name, size?) writes Image + ImageRectOffset
--  + ImageRectSize on an existing ImageLabel. If the network load
--  fails ( offline executor ), we fall back to a curated short
